---
import ShareableQuote from "../../ShareableQuote.astro";
---

<section
    id="positive-security"
    class="relative text-[#e7e5e4] font-serif min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-12 md:py-24 border-b border-emerald-900/10"
>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1 space-y-6">
            <span
                class="text-emerald-500/80 text-xs md:text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase block trigo-positive-chapter"
                >La Seguridad</span
            >
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4]">El Fin del Miedo</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-[#d6d3d1] leading-relaxed">
                La vida nómada era una apuesta diaria. Si no cazabas, no comías. El trigo trajo algo
                nuevo: <strong class="text-emerald-400">El Futuro</strong>.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base text-[#a8a29e] leading-relaxed">
                Por primera vez, la humanidad podía mirar al mañana con certeza. El granero lleno
                significaba que el invierno ya no era una sentencia de muerte. <ShareableQuote
                    quote="Cambiamos la libertad salvaje por la paz mental."
                />
            </p>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 pt-4">
                <div class="text-center p-4 bg-[#1c1917] rounded-lg border border-emerald-900/20">
                    <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-500 mb-1">365</div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-[#a8a29e] uppercase tracking-wider">Días seguros</div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center p-4 bg-[#1c1917] rounded-lg border border-emerald-900/20">
                    <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-500 mb-1">0</div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-[#a8a29e] uppercase tracking-wider">Hambrunas</div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center p-4 bg-[#1c1917] rounded-lg border border-emerald-900/20">
                    <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-500 mb-1">100%</div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-[#a8a29e] uppercase tracking-wider">Certeza</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="order-1 md:order-2 relative h-[500px] flex items-center justify-center">
            <div
                class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-emerald-900/20 via-transparent to-transparent"
            >
            </div>

            <div class="relative w-full max-w-[300px]">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-emerald-500/10 blur-3xl rounded-full"></div>

                <div
                    class="relative bg-gradient-to-b from-[#1c1917] to-[#0c0a09] rounded-2xl border-2 border-emerald-900/30 p-8 overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-emerald-500/50 to-transparent"
                    >
                    </div>

                    <div class="relative z-10 space-y-6">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-emerald-500/60 text-sm">
                            <span>Capacidad</span>
                            <span>100%</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="space-y-3">
                            <div class="h-12 bg-emerald-900/20 rounded-lg relative overflow-hidden">
                                <div
                                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500/40 to-emerald-600/40 animate-pulse"
                                    style="width: 85%"
                                >
                                </div>
                                <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                                    <svg
                                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                        fill="none"
                                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                        stroke-width="1.5"
                                        stroke="currentColor"
                                        class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-400"
                                    >
                                        <path
                                            stroke-linecap="round"
                                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                                            d="M12 3v2.25m6.364.386l-1.591 1.591M21 12h-2.25m-.386 6.364l-1.591-1.591M12 18.75V21m-4.773-4.227l-1.591 1.591M5.25 12H3m4.227-4.773L5.636 5.636M15.75 12a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0z"
                                        ></path>
                                    </svg>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="h-12 bg-emerald-900/20 rounded-lg relative overflow-hidden">
                                <div
                                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500/40 to-emerald-600/40 animate-pulse"
                                    style="width: 92%; animation-delay: 0.3s"
                                >
                                </div>
                                <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                                    <svg
                                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                        fill="none"
                                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                        stroke-width="1.5"
                                        stroke="currentColor"
                                        class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-400"
                                    >
                                        <path
                                            stroke-linecap="round"
                                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                                            d="M12 3v2.25m6.364.386l-1.591 1.591M21 12h-2.25m-.386 6.364l-1.591-1.591M12 18.75V21m-4.773-4.227l-1.591 1.591M5.25 12H3m4.227-4.773L5.636 5.636M15.75 12a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0z"
                                        ></path>
                                    </svg>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="h-12 bg-emerald-900/20 rounded-lg relative overflow-hidden">
                                <div
                                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500/40 to-emerald-600/40 animate-pulse"
                                    style="width: 78%; animation-delay: 0.6s"
                                >
                                </div>
                                <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                                    <svg
                                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                        fill="none"
                                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                        stroke-width="1.5"
                                        stroke="currentColor"
                                        class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-400"
                                    >
                                        <path
                                            stroke-linecap="round"
                                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                                            d="M12 3v2.25m6.364.386l-1.591 1.591M21 12h-2.25m-.386 6.364l-1.591-1.591M12 18.75V21m-4.773-4.227l-1.591 1.591M5.25 12H3m4.227-4.773L5.636 5.636M15.75 12a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0z"
                                        ></path>
                                    </svg>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="pt-4 border-t border-emerald-900/20 text-center">
                            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-500/60 mb-2">
                                Reserva Estratégica
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-400">Granero</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
